# Brent & Co. Data Extractor -- environment template
# Author: AbhishekAEDan
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this file to ".env"  (keep the same folder)
#   2. Paste your own Gemini API key after the "=" below
#   3. Save. The app reads it automatically. Never commit the real .env.
#
# You can also set the key from inside the app:
#   run it -> menu option "3) Change Gemini API key".
# Or set a system environment variable named GEMINI_API_KEY instead.
#
# Get a key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey

GEMINI_API_KEY=
